high_descs: Go to the table next to the door.
Pick up the knife closest to the plate on the table.
Move to face the loaf of bread on the table.
Slice the bread on the table.
Take the knife to the sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Go back to the table with the sliced bread.
Pick up a slice of bread.
Go to the microwave.
Heat the bread in the microwave.
Go to the counter to the right of the sink.
Set the hot bread down on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a hot slice of bread on the counter next to the sink.

high_descs: Turn left then face the table on your right.
Take the knife off of the table in front of you.
Face the bread on the table in front of you.
Slice the bread on the table in front of you.
Turn right and face the sink in front of you.
Place the knife in the sink in front of you.
Turn around and face the table to your right.
Take a bread slice off of the table in front of you.
Turn right and face the microwave near the sink in front of you.
Heat up the bread in the microwave in front of you, take it out and close the microwave.
Turn around and face the counter to your left.
Place the slice of bread on the counter in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a warm slice of bread on the counter.

high_descs: Go to the wooden table across form you.
Pick up the knife that runs parallel with the loaf of bread.
Move back from the table slightly.
Cut the loaf of bread on the table into slices.
Turn to your right and go to the sink. .
Place the knife in the sink.
Turn around and go back to the wooden table ahead, to your left
Pick up one of the slices of bread from the table.
Turn to your right and go to the microwave to the left of the sink.
Place the slice of bread in the microwave, heat it up, then remove the slice of bread from the microwave.
Turn around and go to the counter top to the right of the sink.
Place the slice of bread on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife in the sink and a warm slice of bread on the counter.
